<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Lighten1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Lighten,</orth> to make less heavy, to cheer: <cit><quote>--s my humour with his merry jests,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 1.2.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 2, 21</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>that we may l. our own hearts and our wives' heels,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 5.4.120" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 4, 120</bibl></cit>.
